Package: MIRA
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2017-03-30
Title: Methylation-Based Inference of Regulatory Activity
Description: measures the degree of "dip" in methylation
    level surrounding a regulatory site of interest, such as a 
    transcription factor binding site.
